## Use Cases

The framework includes three benchmark tasks:

### UC1 — RC Low-Pass Filter
- Frequency-domain behavior
- Gain constraints at specific frequencies
- Sensitivity to loading effects

### UC2 — Impedance Matching Network
- L-network design
- Input impedance and reflection coefficient
- Complex-valued measurements

### UC3 — RC Snubber Design
- Transient over-voltage mitigation
- Peak voltage reduction
- Energy dissipation analysis

